<h3 >Wondering what career you should pursue?</h3>

        _CF_FirstErrorField = null;

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['FirstName'], "TEXT", false ) )

            {

                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

            _CF_error_exists = true;

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['LastName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element LastName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['LastName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;

            _CF_error_exists = true;

            //form element Email 'EMAIL' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkEmail(_CF_this['Email'].value, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

            _CF_error_exists = true;

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['UserPassword'], "PASSWORD", false ) )
        {
            //form element UserPassword 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
            _CF_error_exists = true;

        if( _CF_error_exists )

                { _CF_this[_CF_FirstErrorField].focus(); }

            }
            return false;
        }else {
            // run userdefined onSubmit javascript. 
            return masterValidateFunction(this)
            return true;

        _CF_FirstErrorField = null;

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['FirstName'], "TEXT", false ) )

                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

            _CF_error_exists = true;

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['LastName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element LastName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['LastName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))

                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");

            //form element Email 'EMAIL' validation checks

                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['UserPassword'], "PASSWORD", false ) )
        {
            //form element UserPassword 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
            _CF_error_exists = true;

	<h1 align="center">398 Job Descriptions that Start with the Letter "E"</h1>








<hr align="center" >

      <a href="https://www.careerplanner.com/How-To-Write-The-Perfect-Resume.cfm?Loc=centermenu1&amp;AdvertID=CenterMenu4" rel="nofollow"><strong>4) Is your resume getting you enough interviews? Learn <em>How To Write The Perfect Resume</em>.</strong></a></p>

	<h1 align="center">72 Job Descriptions that Start with the Letter "J"</h1>

            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))

                _CF_error_exists = true;

            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))

                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;

            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");

            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))

                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;

        _CF_FirstErrorField = null;

        //form element FirstName required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['FirstName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {

            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['FirstName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "FirstName", _CF_this['FirstName'].value, "Please correct First Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['LastName'], "TEXT", false ) )

            //form element LastName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['LastName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");

            //form element Email 'EMAIL' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkEmail(_CF_this['Email'].value, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

            _CF_error_exists = true;

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['UserPassword'], "PASSWORD", false ) )
        {
            //form element UserPassword 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
            _CF_error_exists = true;

            return masterValidateFunction(this)

    _CF_checkJobFinderForm = function(_CF_this)
    {
        //reset on submit
        _CF_error_exists = false;
        _CF_error_messages = new Array();
        _CF_error_fields = new Object();
        _CF_FirstErrorField = null;

        //form element FirstName required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['FirstName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element FirstName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['FirstName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "FirstName", _CF_this['FirstName'].value, "Please correct First Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "FirstName", _CF_this['FirstName'].value, "Please correct First Name");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element LastName required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['LastName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element LastName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['LastName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element Email required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['Email'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element Email 'EMAIL' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkEmail(_CF_this['Email'].value, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element UserPassword required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['UserPassword'], "PASSWORD", false ) )
        {
            //form element UserPassword 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }


        //display error messages and return success
        if( _CF_error_exists )
        {
            if( _CF_error_messages.length > 0 )
            {
                // show alert() message
                _CF_onErrorAlert(_CF_error_messages);
                // set focus to first form error, if the field supports js focus().
                if( _CF_this[_CF_FirstErrorField].type == "text" )
                { _CF_this[_CF_FirstErrorField].focus(); }

            }
            return false;
        }else {
            // run userdefined onSubmit javascript. 
            return masterValidateFunction(this)
            return true;
        }
    }
//-->
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
<!--
    _CF_checkJobFinderForm = function(_CF_this)
    {
        //reset on submit
        _CF_error_exists = false;
        _CF_error_messages = new Array();
        _CF_error_fields = new Object();
        _CF_FirstErrorField = null;

        //form element FirstName required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['FirstName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element FirstName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['FirstName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "FirstName", _CF_this['FirstName'].value, "Please correct First Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "FirstName", _CF_this['FirstName'].value, "Please correct First Name");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element LastName required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['LastName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element LastName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['LastName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element Email required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['Email'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element Email 'EMAIL' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkEmail(_CF_this['Email'].value, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element UserPassword required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['UserPassword'], "PASSWORD", false ) )
        {
            //form element UserPassword 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }


        //display error messages and return success
        if( _CF_error_exists )
        {
            if( _CF_error_messages.length > 0 )
            {
                // show alert() message
                _CF_onErrorAlert(_CF_error_messages);
                // set focus to first form error, if the field supports js focus().
                if( _CF_this[_CF_FirstErrorField].type == "text" )
                { _CF_this[_CF_FirstErrorField].focus(); }

            }
            return false;
        }else {
            // run userdefined onSubmit javascript. 
            return masterValidateFunction(this)
            return true;
        }
    }
//-->
</script>
</head>

    {

        _CF_error_exists = false;

        _CF_error_fields = new Object();
        _CF_FirstErrorField = null;

        //form element FirstName required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['FirstName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element FirstName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['FirstName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "FirstName", _CF_this['FirstName'].value, "Please correct First Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "FirstName", _CF_this['FirstName'].value, "Please correct First Name");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element LastName required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['LastName'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element LastName 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['LastName'].value, /^[a-zA-Z-]+$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "LastName", _CF_this['LastName'].value, "Please correct Last Name");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element Email required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['Email'], "TEXT", false ) )
        {
            //form element Email 'EMAIL' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkEmail(_CF_this['Email'].value, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "Email", _CF_this['Email'].value, "Please correct the Email address");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }

        //form element UserPassword required check
        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['UserPassword'], "PASSWORD", false ) )
        {
            //form element UserPassword 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
        }


        //display error messages and return success
        if( _CF_error_exists )
        {
            if( _CF_error_messages.length > 0 )
            {
                // show alert() message
                _CF_onErrorAlert(_CF_error_messages);
                // set focus to first form error, if the field supports js focus().
                if( _CF_this[_CF_FirstErrorField].type == "text" )
                { _CF_this[_CF_FirstErrorField].focus(); }

            }
            return false;
        }else {
            // run userdefined onSubmit javascript. 
            return masterValidateFunction(this)
            return true;
        }

            //form element Email 'EMAIL' validation checks

                _CF_error_exists = true;

        if( _CF_hasValue(_CF_this['UserPassword'], "PASSWORD", false ) )
        {
            //form element UserPassword 'REGULAR_EXPRESSION' validation checks
            if (!_CF_checkregex(_CF_this['UserPassword'].value, /^[a-zA-Z0-9]{6,10}$/, true))
            {
                _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
                _CF_error_exists = true;
            }

        }else {
            _CF_onError(_CF_this, "UserPassword", _CF_this['UserPassword'].value, "Please correct your Password");
            _CF_error_exists = true;
